        <h1>Welcome to MicroNest</h1>
        <p>MicroNest is a cutting-edge application that showcases the capabilities of modern microservices architecture using .NET Core. The project aims to provide a scalable, maintainable, and flexible platform for managing products and orders efficiently.</p>
        <p>Our application leverages multiple microservices, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>ProductService</strong>: Manages product-related operations.</li>
            <li><strong>OrderService</strong>: Handles order processing and tracking.</li>
            <li><strong>API Gateway</strong>: Ensures secure and efficient communication between services.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This architecture allows for independent deployment and scaling of each service, optimizing resource management and simplifying updates.</p>
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Comprehensive product management with CRUD operations</li>
            <li>Real-time order management and tracking</li>
            <li>Secure routing via API Gateway</li>
            <li>Responsive design using Tailwind CSS</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>ASP.NET Core 7.0 MVC for robust backend services</li>
            <li>Entity Framework Core for effective data management</li>
            <li>Ocelot API Gateway for secure service routing</li>
            <li>Tailwind CSS for modern, responsive UI design</li>
            <li>Node.js for additional server-side operations</li>
            <li>N-Tier Architecture for organized and scalable code structure</li>
        </ul>
